nodes.name: Anischedule
nodes.description: Displays current, past, and upcoming anime seasons and what anime are airing. Shows information for each anime such as official airing date, description, and when the next episode comes out.

nodes.name: HardwareSwap
nodes.description: Buy, sell, and trade hardware with users around the country. HardwareSwap allows users to create accounts, make listings, and comment on other peoples post. Post are sent to firestore and displayed on the page. Inspired by /r/HardwareSwap.

nodes.name: Country Knowledge
nodes.description: Displays information on every country using https://restcountries.eu API. Each country has its own page that gives information such as region, population, and borders.

nodes.name: GitProfile
nodes.description: Enter a Github username to pull data using Github's API about that user. Data includes your username, followers, stars, and all of your repositories.

nodes.name: Tasks Among Us
nodes.description: You can select any of the current Among Us maps and view all the tasks within a given map. It shows the type of task such as common and where it is located on that map.
